  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Suiton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 10 (Spell Level 5)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 12</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 25 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 13 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 27</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> H, F</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>Your Chakra forms a swirling sphere of water that moves 75 ft. per round in a straight line until it reaches the technique's maximum range. Any Medium-size or smaller creature struck by the orb must succeed at a Reflex save or get dragged along, suffering 3d6 Water damage each round, though it is allowed a Reflex save or swim check every round to escape from the sphere of liquid. Large or larger creatures are merely pushed back 1d6x5 ft. on a failed Reflex save. Structures hit by the sphere take double damage.<br><br>An electric technique that hits the sphere charges it for d4+1 rounds, letting it deal 1d4 electric damage per 2 ranks of the technique to each creature or structure hit by the sphere.<br><br>If the sphere collides with the effects of another Daibakufu or a Suishouha, Deishouha or Bakusuishouha, the effects cancel each other out.</p>\n\n\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
